com.bullhornsdk.data.api.helper

Interface RestCredentials

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Entity<String>

    public interface RestCredentials
extends Entity<String>
    Used to capture RestCredentials in the case of multi-tenant apps. Can be used in RestApiSession as an alternative way of instantiating a session.
    Author:
    Magnus Fiore Palm
